=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LatoocarfianN_ex3 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark clean sound, with complex oscillator character around 1838 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, energy distribution is front_heavy, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: front_heavy

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1837.9174
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.6170
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5687
  pitch_clarity: 6.6908
  inharmonicity: 0.0009
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -2.9742
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

